<section id="itsm_localeFilterType">
    <title>localeFilterType</title>
    
    <para>LocaleFilterType - the <code>localeFilterType</code> attribute is the
            <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink> defined
            <code>localeFilterType</code> attribute. See the <ulink
            url="https://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#localefilter-local">localeFilterType</ulink>
        definition in the <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink>
        specification for details on the purpose of the attribute and permitted values.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> See the <ulink
            url="https://www.w3.org/TR/its20/#localefilter-local">localeFilterType</ulink>
        definition in the <olink targetdoc="../xliff21.xml" targetptr="ITS20">[ITS]</olink>
        specification.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> "include".</para>
    
    <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
        <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/mrk.xml" targetptr="mrk"
            ><code>&lt;mrk></code></olink> and <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sm.xml"
            targetptr="sm"><code>&lt;sm></code></olink>.</para>
    
    
    <para>See the <olink targetdoc="../../modules/itsm/Locale_Filter.xml" targetptr="localeFilterAnnotation"
            >ITS Locale Filter Annotation</olink> for the normative usage description of this
        attribute when used inline; advanced Constraints follow from that normative usage
        description.</para>
    
</section>
